<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Không tìm thấy báo cáo – VOX</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/icon.svg">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/icon.png">
  <style>
    *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
    body{font-family:'Segoe UI',-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f8faff 0%,#f0f4ff 50%,#faf5ff 100%);min-height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column}
    .main{flex:1;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:48px 16px}
    .card{text-align:center;max-width:440px;width:100%}
    .icon-wrap{position:relative;width:128px;height:128px;margin:0 auto 32px}
    .icon-circle{width:128px;height:128px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#eef2ff,#f5f3ff)}
    .badge{position:absolute;top:-4px;right:-4px;width:42px;height:42px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:12px;font-weight:900;color:#fff;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#6366f1,#a855f7);box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(99,102,241,.4)}
    h1{font-size:26px;font-weight:800;color:#1e293b;margin-bottom:10px;letter-spacing:-.02em}
    .desc{font-size:14px;color:#64748b;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:12px}
    .hint{font-size:13px;color:#94a3b8;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:32px;padding:12px 16px;background:#f8fafc;border-radius:10px;border:1px solid #e2e8f0}
    .hint strong{color:#475569}
    .btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:12px 28px;border-radius:12px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#4f46e5,#7c3aed);text-decoration:none;box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(99,102,241,.35);transition:opacity .15s}
    .btn:hover{opacity:.88}
    .footer{padding:16px;text-align:center;border-top:1px solid rgba(99,102,241,.08)}
    .footer p{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:11px;color:#94a3b8}
    .footer img{height:16px;opacity:.5}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="main">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="icon-wrap">
        <div class="icon-circle">
          <svg width="54" height="54" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke="#a5b4fc" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.828 10.172a4 4 0 00-5.656 0l-4 4a4 4 0 105.656 5.656l1.102-1.101m-.758-4.899a4 4 0 005.656 0l4-4a4 4 0 00-5.656-5.656l-1.1 1.1"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="badge">404</div>
      </div>

      <h1>Báo cáo không tồn tại</h1>
      <p class="desc">Link chia sẻ bạn đang truy cập đã hết hiệu lực hoặc không tồn tại.</p>
      <div class="hint">
        Có thể link đã bị <strong>thu hồi</strong> bởi người tạo,<br>
        hoặc bạn đang dùng link <strong>cũ</strong> sau khi báo cáo được cập nhật.
      </div>

      <a href="/" class="btn">
        <svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6"/>
        </svg>
        Về trang chủ
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>
      <img src="/vox_logo.svg" alt="VOX">
      · Nền tảng học tập AI
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
